{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0d7d821f29","title":"红军与张学良杨虎城军应同进同退","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3b3e1b34a3","index":0,"year":1937,"month":1,"day":30,"articleId":"0d7d821f29"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji10","name":"毛泽东全集第10卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji10.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji10":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8b0036c315","type":"paragraph","text":"红军与张学良杨虎城军应同进同退","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"0d7d821f29"},{"id":"bf93f1f225","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年1月30日）周、博，洛，王，彭、任”我们意见如下甲、和平是我们基本方针，也是张检的基本方针。乙、但我们与张杨是三位一体，进则同进，退则同退，我们不能独异失去张杨内、向张杨两部表示，我们始终回他们一道，在他们不同意撤兵以前，我们不单独行动，协助他们争取更有利条件。丁、用以上态度争取最后的和平","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"0d7d821f29"},{"id":"97802bbd25","type":"paragraph","text":"毛朱张","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"0d7d821f29"},{"id":"7fb6ca1157","type":"paragraph","text":"三十月二十四时[1]这是毛泽东和朱德、红军总政治委员张国给中共中央派往西安的代表周题来、博古（暴师宪）等的电报[2]洛，招洛雨，即张周天，当时在西安。王，指王祥，当时任红军总政治部主任。彭、任，指彭德怀、任强时，当时分别任红军前故总指挥和政治委员。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"0d7d821f29"}],"page":{"id":"714e9b0ea4","publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"0d7d821f29","start":174,"end":174}}}},"__N_SSG":true}